snippet.title: Moth Kubit – Official Reveal Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Moth Kubit buzzes onto Nintendo Switch next spring!

Take on the role of Moth Kubit in this surreal and satirical RPG! Investigate the mysterious insect mega-corp, bee-friend co-workers, engage in some verbal showdowns, uncover secrets, and shape the story!
 
#MothKubit #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/
